{
  "stem": "311.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had-- we had free--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not a melamed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a teacher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hebrew teacher, they would call it, you know, came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had an hour in-- in the first grade, an hour in the second grade, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let's say there was two classes, or first two classes or second and third, and so far.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the priest had a little more, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a little more than one-- one hour, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had-- maybe they had a bigger budget.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So since we weren't such good kids, they made us stay with the priest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They say we were running around too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and it-- it was funny, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some of them didn't-- didn't remember something, you know, from the Catholic [INAUDIBLE], and he'd say, look, they used to ask us, and we knew it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he'd say, you see?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That Jewish kid knows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You don't know it, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Can you just tell me, was your home-- obviously it was  a kosher home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, Shabbos was special in Krakow, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't care-- even the people who never went to shul, who didn't-- who-- who were whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would never had the guts to get up on a streetcar, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if somebody-- I remember, you know, if you got out on a streetcar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody was around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You looked around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody jumped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then you put your head down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So God forbid somebody sees you, you know, because they're open, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, it was very-- Friday night, I remember-- even a half hour before the [INAUDIBLE] you know, they used to come around and knock.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Shabbos!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Shabbos!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Close the windows!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, all that thing, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This, I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
